    $slugIt = @iconv(&#39;UTF-8&#39;, &#39;ASCII//TRANSLIT&#39;, $slugIt);

[:alnum:] will match any alpha numeric character (including the ones with accent).  
Take a look at [http://php.net/manual/en/book.regex.php][1] for more information on PHP&#39;s POSIX implementation.


  [1]: http://php.net/manual/en/book.regex.php']

